            "body": "There seems to be two problems here:\r\n1. The `syntax on` already loads the buffer before the `BufRead` autocommand is defined.\r\n2. The `BufRead` is triggered by a `bufload()` call inside the Lua ftplugin (from `vim.treesitter.start()`), but ftplugins don't trigger nested autocommands.",
